{"tid":1561030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［行動升級］十月一日外國勢力要求增援","createTime":"2019-09-11T12:26:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T04:05:04.000Z","uid":39291,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"6ce203102f1a1d9d1411f3e55d316a9c262cc47f","tid":1561030,"uid":39291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:26:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">外國勢力聯盟 - FREEHKUSA</span></span><br />\nPost 1:<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379329/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379329/page/1</a><br />\nPost 2: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1459961/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1459961/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nGoFundMe: <a href=\"https://www.gofundme.com/f/g5zsk-hong-kong-supplies?utm_source=customer&amp;utm_medium=copy_link&amp;utm_campaign=p_cp+share-sheet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2Fg5zsk-hong-kong-supplies%3Futm_source%3Dcustomer%26utm_medium%3Dcopy_link%26utm_campaign%3Dp_cp%2Bshare-sheet&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okd5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=95d4a469\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gofundme.com/f/g5zsk-hong-kong-supplies?utm_source=customer&amp;utm_medium=copy_link&amp;utm_campaign=p_cp+share-sheet</a><br />\n<br />\n我們是一群身居外地，但心繫香港的香港兒女。歷時三個月的抗爭，我們見證了官、商、鄉、黑、警的殘暴不仁，加上無數手足的死、傷，內心不免挫折憂愁。但不管黑暗的路有多漫長，我們外國勢力仍然堅持與香港人一起攜手漫步，走過幽谷。本群組成立於七月下旬，有感香港黑警對抗爭者施以無理打壓，於是自發購買物資，希望助有志抗爭者一臂之力。<br />\n<br />\n十月一日將至，支共建國、南丫海難，這個特別的日子在不同人心中有不同的意義。然而，對我們團隊來說，<span style=\"color: red;\">十月一日將會是香港抗爭史上舉足輕重，足以撼動全局的一天</span>。經過前兩次成功的經驗，令我們殷切希望繼續與所有香港人風雨同行。工欲善其事，必先利其器，有感支共建國日將極大機會出現大型抗爭活動，為免前線抗爭者裝備不足而慘遭港共暴力欺壓，本團隊希望能趕及於十月一日前成功採購物資送抵香港，為香港抗爭繼續出一分力。不過，經歷兩次小型籌款及大量採購後，資金早已捉襟見肘。經過內部團隊磋商，成員一致認眾籌是我們現時最理想的出路，亦是確保我們能繼續長遠發展的重要一步。<br />\n<br />\n現附上前兩次籌集資金記錄以及採購資料，謹供參考(詳看附件)。資料的透明公開，是希望大家能信任我們不會浪費香港人的一分一毫，亦是我們往後的方針和宗旨。我們亦會繼續為香港前線購置所需物品，直至抗爭成功。是次眾籌目標為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">5萬美金</span></span>，希望大家能夠慷慨解囊，為香港未來略盡綿力。<br />\n<br />\n另外，雖然我們有特殊的渠道將物資安全及秘密地送抵香港，但考慮到局勢正不斷惡化，如未來因任何原因而導致我們未能有效將物資送抵香港，我們會將餘下捐款全數捐贈至星火同盟支援基金及612人道支援基金，以善用所有捐款，希望大家理解和明白。<br />\n<br />\n當然，我們絕對希望能與香港人行到最後，希望大家能夠相信外國勢力，與我們同行。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Remember, it&rsquo;s NOW or NEVER.</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y4pBz4J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY4pBz4J.jpg&h=9ba67ccc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ePzuaC4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FePzuaC4.jpg&h=cdfff8c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NSJF1G5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNSJF1G5.jpg&h=7f9a1bfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CE4qtm6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCE4qtm6.jpg&h=f16bdde9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sRYVQAr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsRYVQAr.jpg&h=eaf5bb59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWe are a group of overseas Hongkongers who keep our hometown close to our hearts. Throughout the past three months of the anti-extradition bill struggle, we have witnessed the cruelty and brutality of the state, business, village elite, triads, and police. Countless numbers of our comrades have suffered casualties, paining us deeply and causing us great anxiety. But no matter how long this dark road may be, we will continue to stand with Hongkongers every step of the way out of these dire straits. This group was founded at the end of July to buy supplies for protesters in Hong Kong who continue to face unreasonable crackdowns by the Hong Kong Police Force (HKPF).<br />\n<br />\nOctober 1 is fast approaching. It is a date that has different meanings for different people&mdash;it celebrates the founding of the People&rsquo;s Republic of China and it marks the anniversary of the Lamma Island Ferry Collision. We believe that October 1 will be a momentous day in the history of Hong Kong&rsquo;s struggle. After our first two successes, we earnestly hope to continue to stand with Hongkongers. In anticipation of mass protest activities on PRC&rsquo;s National Day, we hope to successfully purchase and ship supplies to Hong Kong before October 1. However, after our first two small fundraisers and purchasing large amounts of supplies, our funds have dried up. After discussions in our internal team, members unanimously agree that crowdfunding is our best solution at this moment and would also be an important step towards guaranteeing our long-term development.<br />\n<br />\nPlease find the records of our past two fundraisers and purchases attached. In publicizing this information transparently, we hope that you will entrust us with your donations and understand that we will never waste a single penny of Hongkongers. This is our guiding principle. We will also continue to purchase necessary supplies for front liners in Hong Kong until the struggle is victorious. The target for this fundraising campaign is<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> $50000 USD</span></span>. We hope that you will find it in your heart to give generously for Hong Kong&rsquo;s future.<br />\n<br />\nOn another note, while we have special channels for transporting supplies securely and secretly to Hong Kong, the situation there continues to deteriorate in unpredictable ways.  If we are not able to deliver supplies to Hong Kong effectively for whatever reason in the future, we will donate the all of remaining funds to Spark Alliance HK and 612 Humanitarian Relief Fund. Of course, we are committed to standing with Hongkongers until the end. We hope you will believe in the power of solidarity from overseas and join us in our effort."},{"pid":"f9160ecc8bcb64ea8b54411c52ddc460a360d6a2","tid":1561030,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:27:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"1f66931f61ef031fc37e789a3dab6970d09df536","tid":1561030,"uid":39291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:27:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;If you&rsquo;re not ready to die for it, put the word &lsquo;freedom&rsquo; out of your vocabulary.&rdquo; &mdash; Malcolm X<br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;&rsquo;If someone puts their hands on you make sure they never put their hands on anybody else again.&rsquo;&rsquo;&mdash;Malcom X</span></span>"},{"pid":"06b5d14bed61796291bad16cbdbcefd656d4e5b1","tid":1561030,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:27:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CQ70tbX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCQ70tbX.jpg&h=ff557822&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"42fe8c6a698df6603cea67db83ae97c4ed9d1b9f","tid":1561030,"uid":149471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:28:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3c70cb1262233df226cfa581a29b2c658cfcd83","tid":1561030,"uid":30668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:29:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6366357275eac0b298294319b8d2914dbda4f2f5","tid":1561030,"uid":39291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:29:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41013a1a4a2263beaad5d874751bf9b163013508","tid":1561030,"uid":15575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:30:17.000Z","msg":"加油，推！"},{"pid":"798c03d5a8fa4007b26b93998887d94e8c7d54f7","tid":1561030,"uid":39291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:31:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"954c8832d626ab282536c46f6f5d6bff8b7401a9","tid":1561030,"uid":39291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:32:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d7976d8cf3c71f46605bae04110b9b1cfaf09f14","tid":1561030,"uid":264369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:32:38.000Z","msg":"建議為區選選區，尤其反自動當選的，各區獨立設一個台<br />\n原因：<br />\n1. 既然冇大台提供可靠懶人包結論，就要期望唔少唔多喜歡睇文字的手足認真閱讀分析 &quot;raw material&quot; ．每台只處理跟各人相關的資料，可以方便大家作出明智決定，亦方便 admin 管理（移動錯台post／垃圾文 etc）<br />\n2. 這兩天有關 歐頌賢 及 任嘉兒 的討論，大家要跟post都已經有Ｄ難度，遲下區多人多時間逼，再加大大班臥底時，肯定亂到九彩，早日作好安排好Ｄ．"},{"pid":"fbc14ed8f37cc4ca4014916339852752ec9ac70c","tid":1561030,"uid":186851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:33:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"00a3002c526bf4ba954f335a6b72cec1d74cfdb6","tid":1561030,"uid":39291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:33:55.000Z","msg":"推到所有人都睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"588513bc47a58fdbbe400aec4e877be477cb1396","tid":1561030,"uid":136785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:35:31.000Z","msg":"推爆佢"},{"pid":"a5c6c9c36b5565899da44692bf86824a8b1ffa7a","tid":1561030,"uid":39291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:35:38.000Z","msg":"推到所有人都睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hk